DAILY COMMANDS:

Command:                        Description:
--------------------------------------------------
cd <path>                       Change directory |
--------------------------------------------------------------------
ls                              List files in the current directory |
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
mv <file/path> <path>           Rename or move some file or path to some path |
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
scp <file> <path>               Safe copy a file to a path |
------------------------------------------------------------
cp <file> <path>                Copy a file to a path |
-------------------------------------------------------
mkdir <name-of-path>            Make a directory |
-----------------------------------------------------------
rmdir <name-of-path>            Remove an empty directory |
----------------------------------------------------------- 
rm <file>                       Remove a file |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
vi/vim <name-of-the-file>       Call the vi/vim file editor to create e file |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

